1
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:10,010
Look who's here, everyone.

2
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,320
Dong.

3
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:15,040
Hello, comrades.

4
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:18,460
Why are you here instead of staying in the hospital?

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,800
I saw you sitting in my seat just now.

6
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:23,720
Are you trying to usurp my position?

7
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:24,320
It was too dusty.

8
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,580
I was wiping it for you.

9
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:28,040
Mentor, don't worry.

10
00:00:28,040 --> 00:00:29,500
Just focus on recovering.

11
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:31,000
When you get better,

12
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:33,160
we can drink together again.

13
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:34,200
Okay.

14
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:35,400
Captain Ma.

15
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:37,980
When you come back, I'll let you scold me.

16
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:39,360
Dong.

17
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:42,920
When you come back, you can keep kicking me, okay?

18
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:43,400
[kicks]

19
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:45,840
You said it yourself.

20
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,040
Only Old Ma can kick you,

21
00:00:48,040 --> 00:00:48,920
kick you hard.

22
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:49,360
Okay.

23
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:53,600
Take care of your health.

24
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:55,280
I'm retiring soon.

25
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:56,320
After I retire,

26
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,560
you have to hang out with me.

27
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,280
This is an order. Yes, sir.

28
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:00,040
Captain Li.

29
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:05,040
What else are you hiding besides your illness?

30
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,560
There's something

31
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:09,010
that has been on my mind for a long time.

32
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:10,840
There's something

33
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,880
I've always wanted to tell you.

34
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:17,240
Actually, I admire you.

35
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,920
You're a bit like me when I first joined the force.

36
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,780
You want to rush into everything,

37
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,640
always trying to prove your worth,

38
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:26,440
and prove you can do better than others.

39
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,240
I understand.

40
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,170
But if you're too obsessed,

41
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,720
it's no longer a motivation.

42
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:34,160
It becomes pressure, right?

43
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:37,720
One day, when you truly understand this,

44
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,380
you will have really grown up.

45
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,759
I believe in you.

46
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:43,160
You can definitely do it.

47
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,160
Let's go have fun.

48
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,360
Let's hurry.

49
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,170
Let's go.

50
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,800
Bye, Uncle.

51
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,320
Don't worry.

52
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,960
Mr. Ma!

53
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,640
Have fun!

54
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,200
When Mr. Li gets back,

55
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,200
we'll go fishing and swimming in Sanya.

56
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,840
Okay.

57
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,440
Do you remember when we met?

58
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,640
In 1997.

59
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,700
Qianye Nightclub.

60
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,040
I saw you.

61
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:46,480
Then let's start with Qianye.

62
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:48,760
Let's talk about Li Na

63
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,690
and Chen Zhaodi.

64
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,640
Chen Zhaodi?

65
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,360
Linda.

66
00:02:57,160 --> 00:03:00,560
I was only 18 then.

67
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,080
I knew nothing.

68
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,300
I just wanted to leave that house.

69
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,880
Hua Weihong said he could take me with him,

70
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,240
but we needed money.

71
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,280
He told me

72
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,120
we'd just rob them

73
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,680
and wouldn't hurt them.

74
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:28,210
I didn't expect him to lie to me.

75
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:32,170
But I really never thought they would kill Linda.

76
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:34,770
I wasn't even there.

77
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:39,040
When I got back, Linda was already dead.

78
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,079
Na.

79
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,960
She was always good to me.

80
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,920
How could I hurt her?

81
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,480
At that time,

82
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,920
I really tried my best to stop them.

83
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:05,480
But how could I fight against three men?

84
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,280
I failed to protect her.

85
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,170
I feel sorry for her.

86
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:19,240
You had a chance to tell me then.

87
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,120
Why didn't you?

88
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,700
I didn't dare call the police.

89
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:28,700
Hua Weihong threatened me, saying we were all involved in the murder.

90
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,960
I had to go with him.

91
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,560
I thought

92
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,640
if I stayed with him,

93
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,440
at least he loved me

94
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,840
and could always protect me.

95
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:50,480
But I didn't expect him to let Hong Jinyi rape me.

96
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:55,960
I was...

97
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,360
I really broke down at that time.

98
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,440
I didn't know what to do.

99
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,170
I don't really remember

100
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,040
what happened next.

101
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,840
But I remember

102
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,770
when we went to Hong Jinyi's house,

103
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,240
I hid that little girl.

104
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,980
I told her to hide and not come out.

105
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,640
I was afraid they would find her.

106
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,370
I wanted to protect her.

107
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:31,320
From beginning to end, I was just Hua Weihong's tool.

108
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,440
His tool to attract rich people.

109
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,960
I am just a victim too.

110
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:42,640
Do you know what my first lesson at the police academy was?

111
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,580
Never empathize with criminals.

112
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,100
Say something useful.

113
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,300
Let's talk about Li Xuebo.

114
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:01,100
I originally wanted to leave with Xuebo,

115
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,960
to get away from Hua Weihong.

116
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:07,440
But I didn't expect Hua Weihong to find out.

117
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,720
He killed Xuebo in a fit of rage.

118
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:17,880
So according to you, you're a victim.

119
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:20,440
You didn't participate in the murder,

120
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,240
only the robbery

121
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,320
and fraud, right?

122
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,900
You could say that.

123
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,640
I'll admit to what I've done.

124
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,440
You said it.

125
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,970
Let's talk about how Li Xuebo died.

126
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:37,560
I already told you.

127
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:40,080
Hua Weihong killed him.

128
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:44,520
But the medical examiner didn't say so.

129
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:48,240
He said Li Xuebo died

130
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,600
after we arrested Hua Weihong.

131
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,280
Either Hua Weihong is lying,

132
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,280
or you are lying.

133
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,580
The body wouldn't lie, right?

134
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:59,840
I didn't see Hua Weihong kill him with my own eyes.

135
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,540
Could he have been lying to me?

136
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,020
Xuebo was still alive when I left.

137
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,680
I could have saved him.

138
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:12,040
What you're saying makes things difficult.

139
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,320
Who killed him then?

140
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,690
Who else is in your gang?

141
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,440
Lu San?

142
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,080
Yes.

143
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,040
It could be him.

144
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,450
He's been following us.

145
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,840
He also threatened me,

146
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,100
and asked me for money.

147
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,900
Lu San is already dead.

148
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:40,800
I didn't know.

149
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,400
The last time I saw him

150
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,200
was several years ago.

151
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:53,360
He said he couldn't stay here anymore.

152
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,320
He had many enemies.

153
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,480
Could it be them?

154
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,180
Cao Aiyuan,

155
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,920
you're lying.

156
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:10,140
Let me tell you about my evidence.

157
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:17,200
Take a look. Is it him?

158
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,280
I think so.

159
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:30,960
Tell me.

160
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,640
Where did you see him?

161
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:36,440
On the opening day of Lily Flower Shop.

162
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,799
We also found...

163
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:45,000
Near the crime scene,

164
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,040
we found the murder weapon used to kill Lu San.

165
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:49,040
It has Cao Aiyuan's fingerprints on it.

166
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:51,100
Do you have anything else to explain?

167
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:03,160
Cao Aiyuan, have you been home in the past two years?

168
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,400
No.

169
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,240
Since I got out,

170
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,980
I haven't contacted them.

171
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,680
But I have.

172
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,280
To find you in the past two years,

173
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:18,140
I visited your family many times.

174
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,480
How are they?

175
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,560
Good. Really good.

176
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,610
They must have been looking for me.

177
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,480
Can I see them?

178
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,800
They definitely haven't been looking for you,

179
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,330
and it would be hard for you to see them.

180
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,240
Your brother is outstanding.

181
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,440
He got into a college in another province,

182
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,900
and your mom went with him.

183
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,780
Do you know what she said before she left?

184
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:48,560
If we catch you,

185
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,080
we should never contact her.

186
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:54,210
You really disappointed your mom.

187
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:08,760
Cao Aiyuan, I'll tell you the truth.

188
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,440
We have evidence that you killed Li Xuebo

189
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,280
and Lu San.

190
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,130
Although you are a suspect,

191
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,370
you have the right to hire a lawyer.

192
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,080
Tell me who you want to contact,

193
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,540
and I'll find them for you.

194
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:46,420
My dad praised me for being smart since I was little,

195
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:47,680
and pretty.

196
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:52,940
I always thought these were good things.

197
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,400
But it turns out,

198
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,520
I was too naive.

199
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,640
In our mediocre little place,

200
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:05,160
these things made me a target of public criticism,

201
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,120
a literal target.

202
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,480
After my dad passed away,

203
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:12,480
I realized

204
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,800
I couldn't waste my life in that place anymore.

205
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,440
Until I met him,

206
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:23,320
I felt seen for the first time.

207
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:28,220
I thought if I tried hard to leave this place,

208
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:30,280
I could live a better life.

209
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,040
But those people,

210
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:36,840
why were they so mean to me?

211
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:40,680
We have never been treated kindly by this society.

212
00:11:41,400 --> 00:11:42,400
So,

213
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:46,360
what gives you the right to ask me to be kind to it?

214
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,440
Cao Aiyuan,

215
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,890
didn't Li Na show you any kindness?

216
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,570
Didn't Li Xuebo show you kindness?

217
00:11:57,480 --> 00:12:00,410
You just use these excuses to cover up your mistakes.

218
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:03,560
You blame the so-called misfortune from your family of origin.

219
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:04,840
But have you ever considered

220
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:07,370
how many families were broken because of you?

221
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:10,120
Isn't Nuannuan innocent?

222
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,410
Aren't Li Na and Li Xuebo innocent?

223
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,640
Cao Aiyuan, let me tell you.

224
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:21,040
You will spend the rest of your life in endless remorse.

225
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:23,280
Because even now, you still don't understand

226
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,440
what true love is.

227
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,440
I confess.

228
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,000
I confess to everything.

229
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,680
Comrades.

230
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:57,120
The case of Cao Aiyuan and Hua Weihong's gang

231
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,840
has lasted for five years

232
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,240
and spanned four provinces.

233
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:02,300
Now it has been successfully solved.

234
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:05,160
Comrade Lin Wei used his perseverance

235
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,530
to uncover the truth layer by layer

236
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:10,440
and bring the criminals to justice.

237
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,500
The organization has decided

238
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:16,360
to award Comrade Lin Wei a second-class merit.

239
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,560
Comrades.

240
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,570
For the successful resolution

241
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,720
of this case,

242
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:50,280
we must always remember one person.

243
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:53,170
That is Comrade Ma Guodong.

244
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:55,480
In this case,

245
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:59,640
Comrade Ma Guodong also made a huge contribution.

246
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:00,840
Now,

247
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:04,640
all the suspects involved have been brought to justice.

248
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:06,440
The organization has decided to

249
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:10,240
award Comrade Ma Guodong a Second-Class Merit

250
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,780
and posthumously grant him the title of martyr.

251
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:40,040
Not bad, kid.

252
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,770
You worked overtime all night.

253
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,000
Good job.
